339
00:21:08,804 --> 00:21:09,864
You and Brooke, huh?

340
00:21:09,926 --> 00:21:12,219
Yeah. I did not see that coming.

341
00:21:13,132 --> 00:21:17,508
Oh, by the way, if this basketball thing doesn't work out, you may have a future as a painter.

342
00:21:23,375 --> 00:21:27,032
