343
00:21:27,103 --> 00:21:27,918
Yeah.

344
00:21:29,054 --> 00:21:30,421
Yeah, we do.

345
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:32,895
Yeah.

346
00:21:33,402 --> 00:21:37,678
Well, uh, I guess I'll beat the beach tonight.

347
00:21:37,769 --> 00:21:39,494
