348
00:21:42,238 --> 00:21:43,043
Yeah.

349
00:21:51,004 --> 00:21:52,114
You've changed.

350
00:21:53,717 --> 00:21:54,497
Yeah.

351
00:21:55,648 --> 00:21:57,293
I guess I have you to thank for that.

352
00:22:35,566 --> 00:22:38,662
