353
00:22:38,713 --> 00:22:41,324
But who knows? Somedy might go for the homeless-girl look.

354
00:22:41,405 --> 00:22:43,136
You know I don't even want to go to this thing.

355
00:22:43,198 --> 00:22:45,456
I know. But because Mouth is throwing himself

356
00:22:45,507 --> 00:22:47,662
his own personal pity party over Erica Marsh,

357
00:22:47,703 --> 00:22:50,841
you, P. Sawyer, as you know, are my D.J.

358
00:22:51,267 --> 00:22:55,082
Besides, this is the last end-of-summer beach party we're gonna have before we're seniors.

359
00:22:55,132 --> 00:22:57,663
Oh, come on. You know you were gonna have another chance next year

360
00:22:57,703 --> 00:22:59,776
after you flunk out and have to repeat a grade.

361
00:22:59,858 --> 00:23:03,367
See? That's the spirit... sort of.

362
00:23:03,438 --> 00:23:04,773
A little mean, but it's a start.

363
00:23:04,835 --> 00:23:07,395
Speaking of mean, please don't be to Haley tonight, okay?

364
00:23:07,457 --> 00:23:08,215
Let's party.

365
00:23:10,454 --> 00:23:11,305
Come on.

366
00:23:17,384 --> 00:23:18,946
