367
00:23:19,017 --> 00:23:20,472
Can we light the bonfire now?

368
00:23:20,544 --> 00:23:21,762
Can  we? Can we?

369
00:23:21,829 --> 00:23:24,854
Oh, look, it's Tim. I had a dream you died. Darn.

370
00:23:24,911 --> 00:23:26,887
Check it out. I brought some really cool stuff to burn.

371
00:23:26,948 --> 00:23:30,871
