For others -- religion.

384
00:24:53,585 --> 00:24:58,187
But for us, it marks the beginning of our senior year!

385
00:25:02,739 --> 00:25:04,987
I know we have to go back to school soon.

386
00:25:05,033 --> 00:25:10,583
